Text:
Why are all the cute tracks labeled as dark and all the punk tracks labeled as cute? shouldn't it be the other way around..

Worthless MP3 quality. Was a waste to even include it at such a low kbps.

The flacs are good though, thanks

Also, I haven't finished the game yet but is this really all of the music? 

Apart from the menu, credits, and bosses.. 5 compositions for a 23-level game?

I would assume there was at least 3 boss tracks rather than 2 considering there's 3 bosses as well unless they just re-used something for the third boss?

Also, one last thing - this OST is awesome so thanks for the upload.

Will seed.
